Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:53.16,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}絶命の声が風になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:53.16,ED-cht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}绝命之声作风飘散
